Description: MIROC base infrastructure TOUZA (楊座)
 TOUZA (楊座), MIROC base infrastructure, is a collection of Fortran
 procedures mainly adopted in MIROC.
 .
 This package contains an example (still useful) command,
 compiled with the TOUZA library.
 .
   chak - Swiss(CH) Army Knife for gtool-3.5 format files

